          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Stopping Grinch Bots Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the circumvention (e.g.,&nbsp;via bot technology)&nbsp;of a website's security measure or technological control for enforcing posted purchasing limits or for managing inventory. A person may not sell a product if the person knows that the product was acquired using such circumvention.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2018-11-16</actionDate>
        </item>
